text: Cool clouds over Pogonip right now.
author: jasonhoppin

text: This is how reporters let opposition define the narrative. It’s a disservice to the public because it forces everyone to focus on the negatives about candidates. Democracy loses.
author: jasonhoppin

text: Media running with the thinnest smears on Beto (“He said his wife raised their kids!”) tells me they learned nothing from 2016 and we’re in for a long 2020 campaign.
author: jasonhoppin
